  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This research proposes a pilot study using the combination of continuous glucose monitor&#xD;
      (CGM) and insulin pump therapy, also known as sensor augmented pump (SAP) therapy, for cystic&#xD;
      fibrosis related diabetes (CFRD) management in the inpatient setting, with the aim of&#xD;
      improving glycemic control.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
